Module Name: POS Tagging using HMM and Viterbi Algorithm

1- Requirements:
----------------
 Operating System               :       LINUX (tested on <= Ubuntu 12.04)

 Compiler/Interpreter/Librarie(s):      g++ / Perl  / Python



2- How to run
---------------
python viterbi.py <testfile> <trainfile>


viterbi.py - input is the test sentences and output is the tagged sentences.

emmission.py - calculates the probabilities of an word 'W' being tagged 'T' 

transition.py - calucates the prabability of tag 'T2' following tag 'T1'  


